{
  "texts": [
    "For a fair comparison, all RL-based methods are trained with 100,000 episode data, and all LLM-based methods are trained with 100 episode data.",
    "For model-based RL methods DORL, we use the same DeepFM model as [15].",
    "For the Reflection and BiLLP methods, we set the number of most similar reflections 𝐾 = 2.",
    "For the BiLLP method, we set the similarity threshold 𝜏 𝐴 = 0.01 and 𝜏 𝐶 = 0.1.",
    "The discount factor 𝛾 is set to 0.5."
  ]
}